init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A general sense of uncertainty and anxiety is pervading the globe.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Dads everywhere are speaking to the good Lord about how things can be changed and how he can help them with their respective families.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: On the flip-side, many businesses are paying men to stay at home.
